is]]<ref>{{cite book |last=Douglas |first=Allen |title=From fascism to libertarian communism: Georges Valois against the Third Republic |year=1992 |publisher=University of California Press |pages=14–15}}</ref>{{·}}[[Arthur Moeller van den Bruck|van den Bruck]]{{·}}[[Gianni Vattimo|Vattimo]]{{·}}[[Max Weber|Weber]]{{·}}[[Robert Anton Wilson|Wilson]]<ref>{{cite book |url= http://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=r-7gZkPoeMY |title=Robert Anton Wilson talks about Alfred Korzybski, Friedrich Nietzsche,...}}</ref>{{·}}[[Bernard Williams|Williams]]{{·}}[[Arnold Zweig|Zweig]]{{sfn|Golomb|1997}}{{Rp|needed=yes|date=March 2012}}
